{"tid":1385000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致：如今還不肯罷工的香港人","createTime":"2019-07-30T03:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T07:42:25.000Z","uid":14262,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e83ba828a57cfbd35d48a2fbde2513554ce6325e","tid":1385000,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:41:03.000Z","msg":"6月9至今，五大訴求一樣都未得到正面回應。<br />\n<br />\n和理非盡了他們最大能力，每星期和平遊行表達訴求、道歉行動、遍地開花的Lennon Wall、每一次文宣工作。<br />\n<br />\n勇武亦不斷賽後檢討，每一次行動都變得成熟和進步。但奈何亦有樽頸時候。<br />\n<br />\n如果再不轉型做罷工抗爭模式，<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不幸被政權逼死的人，帶著遺憾。<br />\n身受重傷的義士，白白流血。<br />\n被捕的抗爭者，坐上政治冤獄。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n以上都是為你走出來，勇敢對抗港共政府。<br />\n<br />\n這次如果不幸輸了，相信未來再沒有人為你發聲。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">社會靠人民運作，政府是人民公僕。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n主權絕對係你地手上。<br />\n<br />\n眼見社會各樣不公不義，<br />\n如還有良知，請為你自己和下一代站出來罷工，<br />\n去推翻這個腐敗醜惡的政府。"},{"pid":"92b951e5089125790866256e5732ed3ed6b2a146","tid":1385000,"uid":14262,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:45:56.000Z","msg":"如其他手足巴抗所講，今次輸咗，真係永不翻身。<br />\n<br />\n而且今次革命，比中共試晒你地香港人底線。<br />\n<br />\n所有野做到出晒面，警黑聯手，唔跟足指引開槍等等<br />\n<br />\n香港人仍然吞聲忍氣，又或者視若無睹。<br />\n<br />\n未來兩三年，一定會產生巨變。<br />\n<br />\n再無法發起社運，面對社會信用評分，上網要翻牆等等"},{"pid":"d081fe0649ddff94c10b6f04c33561f7a0ec7258","tid":1385000,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:46:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如其他手足巴<span style=\"color: red;\">打</span>所講，今次輸咗，真係永不翻身。<br />\n<br />\n而且今次革命，比中共試晒你地香港人底線。<br />\n<br />\n所有野做到出晒面，警黑聯手，唔跟足指引開槍等等<br />\n<br />\n香港人仍然吞聲忍氣，又或者視若無睹。<br />\n<br />\n未來兩三年，一定會產生巨變。<br />\n<br />\n再無法發起社運，面對社會信用評分，上網要翻牆等等</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d38828d4881154e9da4afe8f10207c89b9cbc87e","tid":1385000,"uid":216426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:48:14.000Z","msg":"巴打們 我求你地入泥睇睇<br />\n求你地幫我推<br />\n我想休息一下 <br />\n日頭去夢遊 夜晚就推post<br />\n我就係想頭一頭<br />\n<br />\n雙普選比獨立調查更重要<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379266</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f0dca7ce5e874acbdeb7ed16477329e25ffb339f","tid":1385000,"uid":14262,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:50:39.000Z","msg":"如果去到8月，都發起唔到罷工。<br />\n<br />\n對唔住，我真係灰晒心"},{"pid":"e007ce62820478aef2ec877800f2249f01c9c40d","tid":1385000,"uid":14262,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:55:00.000Z","msg":"自私活下去，繼續辜負年輕人"},{"pid":"23f5b72d44eb29ac5766c83c8bc1b8f99276f93a","tid":1385000,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/main/contact_us.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fch%2Fcustomer%2Fmain%2Fcontact_us.html&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI3aXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=175ba80e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/main/contact_us.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">狗鐵投訴熱線</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/30/100800_1307ec929544e214dd394c87b2dd2854.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F30%2F100800_1307ec929544e214dd394c87b2dd2854.gif&h=cca6589b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50fb448046cc6237dcb6ddebc643b160c59a76bb","tid":1385000,"uid":278443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:56:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4f6208494b0381d97d386f76ee1e2e8fa3e257b","tid":1385000,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06344bed365eb88a909bdaeba581c2d038c32f10","tid":1385000,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:57:18.000Z","msg":"趕狗入窮巷必遭反<br />\n<br />\n不肯罷工既人衰過狗<br />\n<br />\n你地下一代生活，每朝早都要爹親娘親，不及習近平親。<br />\n<br />\n家家戶戶都要有一幅習近平照"},{"pid":"1e7abfc64e46cf30a5f09f6556ae7c06e88d47eb","tid":1385000,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:02:34.000Z","msg":"再唔走出黎，冇人再發你發聲，冇人為你企出黎。<br />\n<br />\n你下一代生活在香港市呢個''福地''，有事搵警察被抗於門外。人民生活受唔到應有保障。你子女辛辛苦苦搵埋血汗錢，去進貢比習大大。"},{"pid":"c9568dc7a5216edd3a86980585162e454b73db7c","tid":1385000,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:04:39.000Z","msg":"負評既出黎講句啊！<br />\n<br />\n50年不變係一個笑話，一半都未過，一國兩際已經腐蝕晒<br />\n<br />\n一國兩際只係變咗外交官員用黎搬龍門既方法。"},{"pid":"857eac3240733f35987b99fbf192ab67d43d914f","tid":1385000,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:05:34.000Z","msg":"唔撚推啦，睇到就睇，反正醒咗既都醒咗。"},{"pid":"f8b22d301791a19cbdbe4b5b1089bc4cc62eb0f8","tid":1385000,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kQabLNW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkQabLNW.jpg&h=343d2412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幫你整咗張文宣圖 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd556dbc3db92689deb16da07aa9aa004530c85f","tid":1385000,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8b22d301791a19cbdbe4b5b1089bc4cc62eb0f8","tid":1385000,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kQabLNW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkQabLNW.jpg&h=343d2412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幫你整咗張文宣圖 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:32:39.000Z","msg":"多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我文筆好差，本身純粹發洩心中不憤同鬧醒香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c9bb03ce46b639917d22a610f96bbefe67a038","tid":1385000,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,