img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會證明到香港有好多人都支持依個運動<br />\n加油！可以失望,但不能絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a027ea8b7f281f732ff97a871ba1a1ac37be2cc7","tid":1385000,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9888f56c56eacb7e6c8b1b3a6e35703437d2b4e3","tid":1385000,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67c9bb03ce46b639917d22a610f96bbefe67a038","tid":1385000,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8b22d301791a19cbdbe4b5b1089bc4cc62eb0f8","tid":1385000,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kQabLNW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkQabLNW.jpg&h=343d2412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幫你整咗張文宣圖 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:38:04.000Z","msg":"如果罷工運動，我真係好會心灰<br />\n<br />\n政府，警察一切持續既惡行唔會令我灰<br />\n<br />\n最令我無望既，係香港人唔支持香港人。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:53:08.000Z","msg":"唔洗灰心, 即使罷工唔成功, 仲有好多方法去抗爭<br />\n我會做多啲文宣希望可以令到多啲人參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會證明到香港有好多人都支持依個運動<br />\n加油！可以失望,但不能絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:01:35.000Z","msg":"遊行唔理，勇武而血喚醒港人又叫唔醒<br />\n<br />\n罷工真係唯一既路，亦係最後手段<br />\n<br />\n唔成功基本輸咗八成，只係覺得好對不起所有義士<br />\n<br />\n發過夢上過前場都知，佢地最有良知、有愛心、好善良既人，我敢講係香港最高質既一群人。<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解佢地要受傷要坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢地都係想社會變好，為自由為民主而戰。"},{"pid":"62112e2ce3acba9ae9cba439d4c8478b6e57c1ec","tid":1385000,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:24:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb95b739f288a5dc5edb5b8256bfd513458a16e9","tid":1385000,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src